  Shell "rm -rf " & Shell$(sDir) Wait

  AddLog(("Creating .spec file."))

  hFile = Open $sHome &/ "RPM/SPECS" &/ $sPackageName & ".spec" For Create

  Print #hFile, "%define name " & $sPackageName
